alo and baboons are all residents here</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-1309310869-headingOne\" class=\"accordion-header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a class=\"accordion-button\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #313041; appearance: button; position: relative; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 733.344px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 18px; background: none; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; overflow-anchor: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; box-shadow: none; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border-color: #ebe6de #ebe6de initial #ebe6de; border-style: solid solid initial solid;\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#acc-item-1309310869-collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panelsStayOpen-collapseOne\">Day 2: Nakuru &ndash; Masai Mara</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-1309310869-collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-color: #ebe6de; border-image: initial; border-radius: 0px 0px 8px 8px; border-style: initial solid solid solid;\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-item-1309310869-headingOne\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 30px 6px;\">Departure from the camp soon after breakfast and drive via the scenic floor of the Great Rift Valley to Masai Mara. Lunch at a campsite before proceeding for evening gamedrives.Dinner and overnight stay at camp/lodge</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-2796421226-headingOne\" class=\"accordion-header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a class=\"accordion-button\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #313041; appearance: button; position: relative; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 733.344px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 18px; background: none; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; overflow-anchor: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; box-shadow: none; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border-color: #ebe6de #ebe6de initial #ebe6de; border-style: solid solid initial solid;\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#acc-item-2796421226-collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panelsStayOpen-collapseOne\">Day 3: Maasai Mara</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-2796421226-collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-color: #ebe6de; border-image: initial; border-radius: 0px 0px 8px 8px; border-style: initial solid solid solid;\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-item-2796421226-headingOne\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 30px 6px;\">The full day is spent Exploring the park in search of the big 5 with a possibility of seeing the annual wildebeest migration that takes place from July to October. Optional hot air balloon safari can be arranged at an extra cost of US$ 450.Dinner and overnight stay at camp/lodge The Mara offers wildlife in such variety and abundance that it is difficult to believe: over 450 species of animals have been recorded here. You will easily see lions, rhinos, hippos, crocodiles, giraffe, wildebeests, zebras, buffalo, warthogs, hyenas, jackals, wild dogs, buffalo, leopard, many kinds of antelopes and elephant. It is in the Mara that perhaps the most spectacular event of the natural world takes place. This is the annual migration of millions of wildebeest and zebra from the Serengeti (Tanzania) in search of water and pasture. Following on their heels are the predators of the savanna- lion, cheetah, wild dog, jackal, hyena and vultures</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: none; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-1116638709-headingOne\" class=\"accordion-header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a class=\"accordion-button\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #313041; appearance: button; position: relative; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 733.344px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 18px; background: none; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; overflow-anchor: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; box-shadow: none; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border-color: #ebe6de #ebe6de initial #ebe6de; border-style: solid solid initial solid;\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#acc-item-1116638709-collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panelsStayOpen-collapseOne\">Day 4: Maasai Mara- Nairobi</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-1116638709-collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px 0px 8px 8px; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-color: #ebe6de; border-image: initial; border-style: initial solid solid solid;\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-item-1116638709-headingOne\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 30px 6px;\">Morning game drive then return to the campsite for breakfast . We drive back to Nairobi where the safari ends.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 108, 108, NULL, 2, 30, NULL, NULL, NULL, 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, '690.00', '690.00', NULL, NULL, 1000, NULL, 'publish', NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-12-18 13:45:55', '2023-12-18 13:47:10');
