 solid;\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-item-3823379658-headingOne\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 30px 6px;\">Early breakfast then depart for Mara driving south along the floor of the Great Rift Valley. Lunch en route arriving Mara in the afternoon check in at Mara sopa logde a five star lodge located on the slopes of oloongams hills. It&rsquo;s one of the finest, built in an ethnic design surrounded by a rich landscape have an evening game drive at the diverse Mara having an opportunity to see various animals before they return to their hide outs.Back to the lodge for dinner and an overnight.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-247864751-headingOne\" class=\"accordion-header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a class=\"accordion-button\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #313041; appearance: button; position: relative; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 733.344px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 18px; background: none; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; overflow-anchor: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; box-shadow: none; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border-color: #ebe6de #ebe6de initial #ebe6de; border-style: solid solid initial solid;\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#acc-item-247864751-collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panelsStayOpen-collapseOne\">DAY 2 MARA</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-247864751-collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-color: #ebe6de; border-image: initial; border-radius: 0px 0px 8px 8px; border-style: initial solid solid solid;\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-item-247864751-headingOne\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 30px 6px;\">After breakfast have a full day game drive taking you to searching the big five , antelopes, zebra, giraffe, jackals, cheetah and different species of birds that occur in the reserve. Lunch back for more game drives on the plains are enormous herds of grazing animals plus cat of prey hiding amidst acacia. On request we can organize a visit to the village of the Masai people to witness their singing and dancing which is part of their daily lives. A glimpse to into their homes and social structure is a great experience all together as you enjoy sun set on the vast plains. Back to the lodge for dinner and an overnight.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-4105991055-headingOne\" class=\"accordion-header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a class=\"accordion-button\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #313041; appearance: button; position: relative; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 733.344px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 18px; background: none; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; overflow-anchor: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; box-shadow: none; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border-color: #ebe6de #ebe6de initial #ebe6de; border-style: solid solid initial solid;\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#acc-item-4105991055-collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panelsStayOpen-collapseOne\">DAY 3 MARA /NAKURU</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-4105991055-collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-color: #ebe6de; border-image: initial; border-radius: 0px 0px 8px 8px; border-style: initial solid solid solid;\" aria-labelledby=\"acc-item-4105991055-headingOne\">\r\n<div class=\"accordion-body\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 30px 6px;\">Early breakfast at the lodge a final game drive to see the diurnal animals that are only seen at day time and the beautiful view of sun Donne rising in the reserve. Check out and drive to Lake Nakuru national park arriving in time for lunch at sarova lion hill lodge which is nestled along the lion hill overlooking spectacular pink rimmed lake Nakuru and a panoramic view of the lake. After lunch and a few hours of rest have a evening game drive in the park which has earned a reputation as an important haven for the endangered species-particularly the Roth&rsquo;s child giraffe and the black and white rhino lions water buck baboons buffalo are all residents here. Dinner and an overnight.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"accordion-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: none; margin-bottom: 20px; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-4263270887-headingOne\" class=\"accordion-header\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><a class=\"accordion-button\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #313041; appearance: button; position: relative; display: flex; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; width: 733.344px; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; font-size: 18px; background: none; border-width: 1px 1px 0px; border-image: initial; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; overflow-anchor: none; transition: all 0.2s ease 0s; box-shadow: none; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; border-color: #ebe6de #ebe6de initial #ebe6de; border-style: solid solid initial solid;\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#acc-item-4263270887-collapseOne\" aria-expanded=\"true\" aria-controls=\"panelsStayOpen-collapseOne\">DAY 4 NAKURU</a></div>\r\n<div id=\"acc-item-4263270887-collapseOne\" class=\"accordion-collapse collapse show\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px 1px 1px; border-color: #ebe6de; border-image: initial; border-radius: 0px 0px